Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.98,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Fire safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:08.82,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.94,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a historical drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:13.32,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is what you call Showa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:17.58,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe grade school kids are \Ntalking about nostalgia and the Showa era.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a string of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.33,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the arson cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There was one four days ago, \Nand another two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.50,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,And once every two days means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tonight—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:39.38,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.06,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.37,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? There's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.19,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Something's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:51.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Was that man we saw earlier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.27,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He could be the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:55.07,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.48,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:00.49,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I know that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:01.99,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Solving crimes with sharp detective skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Love and cases never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:15.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The hand of an arsonist sneaks up on a \Nchildren's park free of fire hazards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:19.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:07.96,DCEpTitle,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)}The Pitfall of Fire Precautions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Pitfall of Fire Precautions!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.54,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Genta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.05,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:17.96,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,When I go to buy an eel lunch, he always \Nbuys an extra large seaweed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.60,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.96,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure he's the arsonist \Nfrom yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.97,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,If he's someone else, \Nwe could get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.01,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Series of Fires at Children's Park
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.98,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Culprit on the Run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.98,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth Incident Produces Casualty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.98,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's last year's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.28,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's been bothering me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:36.73,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's been happening at the same places, \Nincluding yesterday's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:40.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're children's parks in \Na three by three kilometer area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The fires started over \Nthe course of two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.69,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Though the fourth case produced a casualty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:52.12,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,and the suspect was never \Narrested, the incidents stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:58.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And one year later, in the same places \Nusing the same methods, it's started again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.15,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a copycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:07.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it could also be that \Nlast year's arsonist is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.60,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Him! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.48,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.13,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely the man from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.24,Suguru,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Kamaishi Suguru (25)\NJob-hopper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.24,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The usual, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.45,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sure thing. Your usual extra large \Nseaweed lunch, coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.45,Harue,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Yatabe Harue (48)\NPart-time Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.82,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Your kinpira is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.02,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.12,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? You're giving me that much extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.59,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.08,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're both left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.04,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.75,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.97,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.80,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,You should eat a salad sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.77,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Have I set a flame in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.64,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the arsonist of forbidden love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.68,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.32,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.89,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.44,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's goofing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.33,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.24,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's expose his true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.91,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys are on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.90,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.98,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.91,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we let the police handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But he was only near the \Nscene of the crime yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:24.44,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll have to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:25.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.95,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.47,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You just had three pork buns \Nfrom the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.99,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I should've had an eel lunch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.26,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:57.00,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do if he goes to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:06:00.20,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,So far the fires have been \Nhappening every other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.74,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,so there might not be one tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.96,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.68,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.22,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.51,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.80,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.07,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:55.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Through the third incident yesterday, the \Nfires have been starting in the same places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If the fourth is about to occur, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.67,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be in the same place as the fourth fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.06,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.79,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.82,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the fourth fire started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, the first victim was found here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:22.65,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,A drunk office worker sleeping while \Nwrapped up in a construction tarp died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.68,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Parks are creepy at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.21,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They should add more lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:33.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's still pretty bright since \Nthere's a high-rise apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:37.83,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,But with all these people living \Nhere, were there really no witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It is on the side of the north-facing alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.38,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.11,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.73,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We escaped by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.17,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.38,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.67,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,The arsonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:12.41,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just saved you. Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.43,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, damn. He got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.57,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what happened yesterday, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:21.79,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:22.88,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.71,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:29.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think this could be \Nrelated to last years fires, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you've been on the lookout?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.12,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.20,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,So why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.80,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.78,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:44.08,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,If it is the same person as last \Nyear, I need to catch him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.62,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you kids, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.71,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.88,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.77,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.42,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for rescuing us from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.69,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for mistaking you for the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.89,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said something sooner, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.50,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.10,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,The same side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.85,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:14.24,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a one-man detective squad who rose up\Nto protect this city from the evil arsonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A one-man detective squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:20.24,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need "squad" \Nif there's only one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.75,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.00,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.00,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:30.80,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.75,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.42,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What about the arsonist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.08,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the one-man detective squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.18,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous for just you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.04,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We should work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.43,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're protecting the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.27,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so standoffish, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.52,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some reason that \Nwouldn't be good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.02,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.87,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.88,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Our new detective team has been formed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.32,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.99,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. I don't have time for kids—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.79,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.89,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:13.80,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.80,Park,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sumire Park
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.38,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the scene of the first fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.10,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Last year that swing was set on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.06,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,And this year it was this seesaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.06,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.12,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're reviewing the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.56,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,For example, how did the fire start?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.48,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll find witnesses to question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.41,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,If there were witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:40.24,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't the police have arrested \Nthe arsonist a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.63,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.03,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.27,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I haven't had breakfast yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.41,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.79,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,You had your breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.17,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I'm already hungry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.42,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.02,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:59.90,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,The police would have already \Nconducted a general investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.14,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsuji Park
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.16,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, these monkey bars were set on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:12.00,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,And that arched bridge was the second fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.94,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.52,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.20,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.12,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:25.20,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Toward Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.20,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not time for lunch yet, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.29,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.19,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.20,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.21,Park2,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Himawari Park
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.21,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the third and the day \Nbefore yesterday's crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.77,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The jungle gym was set on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:36.21,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Last year it was that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.36,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.09,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Eel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.09,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to get some eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.45,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.88,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.60,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Walking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.38,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.25,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.09,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, wow, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.02,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.42,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,And I got extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.69,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we can have some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.84,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.96,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I got paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.00,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.61,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order you some eel liver soup, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.92,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.06,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.71,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.02,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.24,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.33,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.27,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He gave us the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.19,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Gave us the slip? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:42.69,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's some reason \Nhe doesn't want us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.59,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.90,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.45,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! Does that mean he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.38,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,The arsonist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.21,Closed,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.97,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.15,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,How mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:10.72,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It was tasty, but I won't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,His obsession did seem unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.37,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.31,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:22.73,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,If it is the same person as last \Nyear, I need to catch him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.97,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, he's definitely \Nconnected somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.24,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth Incident Produces Casualty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.58,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.13,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.27,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.25,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.22,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.01,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,This is yesterday's crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.94,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.20,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.65,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.67,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,So where did the key figure go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.58,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.41,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday we couldn't see \Nsince it was nighttime,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:22.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but this isn't a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's a countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.80,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:31.05,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,These letters circled in red \Nwere left at every crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.05,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the first scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.63,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:38.51,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,The police would have already \Nconducted a general investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.06,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.83,Houses,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}Houses for Lease
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose you read that character as "to."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:46.57,To,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,1)}To
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the second scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.14,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.83,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.84,Toward,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,960)}Toward Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.83,To,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,1)}He
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"He."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the third scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.34,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to get some eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.35,Walking,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,960)}Walking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:12.97,To,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,10}Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.40,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the fourth crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.49,Ninja,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,960)}Ninja Fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:21.98,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,1)}{\a6}Ni
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:19.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Ni."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.46,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,To, he, ho, ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:31.36,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it counting down \N"irohanihoheto" backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.41,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Irohanihoheto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.36,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Tohehoni
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. In other words, the \Ncrimes will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning a fifth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.70,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.21,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,But after someone died \Nduring the fourth incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:47.25,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,he was either frightened or scared off by \Nthe investigation, and canceled his plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the fifth crime scene, there's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.48,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,But why does he always \Nchoose children's parks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:56.14,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,And set fire to playground equipment \Nlike seesaws and slides?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.64,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.44,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.65,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.65,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha Toys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.65,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.65,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.54,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.15,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,And on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.03,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They all say Iroha Toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:19.61,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's likely the equipment burned at the other\Nparks were made by the same company, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.57,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.29,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.63,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Their factory is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.33,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.63,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.30,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where the next one will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:34.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the location of the \Nfifth and final fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.06,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's closed because it's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:49.89,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.45,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The arsonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.86,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He's left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.37,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's him after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara, dial 110 and 119.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.42,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:03.86,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:04.61,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:05.79,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The police will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.41,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Edogawa Conan, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:45.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You should give yourself up, \Narsonist and lunch shop lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.28,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.28,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.92,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:56.10,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,They're both left-handed, but she's the \None who could drive that van, not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:02.43,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.69,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.30,DCItalic,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.44,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:12.53,DCItalic,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.19,DCItalic,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,You should eat a salad sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.28,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.42,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.78,Closed,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.15,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.55,DCItalic,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.79,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,A year and a half ago, a child playing \Nat the park was badly injured
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:57.71,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,because of a defect in \Nthe equipment made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.91,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,The company dumped all the blame on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:05.42,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,the factory manager, fired me,\Nand denied all knowledge of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.99,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,It was no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.25,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,You were the factory manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave behind\Nthe Iroha countdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.68,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,To get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.06,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,To make them regret what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:26.76,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd offered a single \Napology, I would have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:31.77,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like you were \Nthe only ones who noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.33,DCMain,HARUE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.23,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.78,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, a man is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.28,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.00,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real? Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.83,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously thought your \Nkinpira was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.29,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.98,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:08.68,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.37,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:14.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You actually witnessed last \Nyear's fourth fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:15.74,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.25,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the kid's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.79,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.56,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.54,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.13,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.45,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.45,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Nearby House Robbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.02,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,A robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:31.80,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.97,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.46,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,He's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And that place was the scene of his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right next to the crime \Nscene where the man died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:48.95,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've quit robbing houses, \Nbut I was afraid of being arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:51.38,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't report it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:56.98,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself I didn't see the arsonist's \Nface clearly and lied to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.50,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,But I always regretted it, thinking \Nthat if I'd turned myself in then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:07.62,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,the arsonist would have been arrested sooner,\Nand that man would have been avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:11.12,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,Then the fires started again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:19.63,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to capture the \Narsonist myself and then turn myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:24.32,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, I'm surprised you noticed, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.68,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,You asked the old man for help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:37.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,When I explained the thief's methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and your actions to him over the phone, \Nthe Sleeping Kogoro figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:42.57,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,The Sleeping Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.04,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:46.82,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could escape him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.17,DCMain,KAMAISHI,0000,0000,0000,,He sure got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:20.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And so, peaceful nights returned to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:25.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The news reported that the \Nplayground equipment accident
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:29.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,that happened a year and a half ago that \Nsparked everything was being re-investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.81,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Fire safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.92,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Fire safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:45.96,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:24:08.96,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.86,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.24,DCMain,EBIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I know about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:56.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:00.64,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I already did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:02.00,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What about this cameraman?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:08.96,DCMain,EBIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who chose Iwami.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:14.97,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Conan and Ebizo's Kabuki Juhachiban Mystery\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:14.74,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "Conan and \NEbizo's Kabuki Juhachiban Mystery, Part One!"
