Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:36.77,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...Detective Conan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:37.70,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...20th anniversary...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.70,0:24:38.70,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...exciting kabuki experience.
